


translate English day5_76b2fe88:


    nvl clear


translate English day5_9d985aa2:


    br "\n I come to under a clear sky.{w} Thick, viscous mud grasps my ankles. The sickly stench of rotten entrails makes my head want to explode.{w}{nw}"


translate English day5_d5419cc9:


    extend "\n A cloth--I don't know whose--hangs over my head, sticky and wet. It's a dream. THE dream. {w}{nw}"


translate English day5_dc18704d:


    extend "The angel dream. A faint light shines into the dark room, and eventually, I hear the sound of the opened door quietly shutting again. {w}{nw}"


translate English day5_42cbc151:


    extend "The momentary flash of light was too bright for me. She has come.{w} Beating her immaculate wings, the angel turns her back to the painful radiance and reaches a slender arm out to me."


translate English day5_c18f18a8:



    nvl clear
    br "\n Despite her clean, pure appearance, the unique stench of this place is awful.{w}{nw}"


translate English day5_3e3289df:


    extend "\n She is an angel. A being so far beyond me that I shouldn't even be able to lock eyes with her, much less touch her. {w}{nw}"


translate English day5_415c6ab2:


    extend "But that is how this world of the two of us works. {w}{nw}"


translate English day5_bc956de4:


    extend "\n\n \"[na2], come and live with me. {w}{nw}"


translate English day5_cbe07c27:


    extend "\nYou needn't go outside anymore. {w}{nw}"


translate English day5_23581097:


    extend "\nYou don't need to force your mind to understand the truths you'd rather not know. {w}{nw}"


translate English day5_f5fdc36d:


    extend "\nYou have no more need for those rotting arms, either, nor for words that convey only lies.\" {w}{nw}"


translate English day5_9a15d8d5:


    extend "\n \"For I shall stay at your side forevermore.\""


translate English day5_76b2fe88_1:


    nvl clear


translate English day5_efdeb305:


    br "\n Ah, what a kind, compassionate being she is. Her warmth is like something I've avoided for a long time, but am finally able to wish for again. {w}{nw}"


translate English day5_42545dd7:


    extend "Our lips touch, and a lukewarm liquid enters my mouth along with her moist tongue. As the liquid drips to the bottom of my throat, I smell something raw, like iron. {w}{nw}"


translate English day5_033f04d9:


    extend "The angel's wings are spread overhead, creating a shadow over my vision. I look up at her, and for some reason, she feels so, so far away. {w}{nw}"


translate English day5_0726615d:


    extend "\n My vision wavers, dizzy, as a dull gray light enters it. {w}{nw}"


translate English day5_6ee1ee40:


    extend "\nBelieving it to be salvation, I close my eyes. Blood scatters across the immaculate woman."


translate English day5_88815579:



    nvl clear
    br "\n Her smile, however, remains unsullied, and she doesn't withdraw the hand she held out to me. {w}{nw}"


translate English day5_0ab27f7c:


    extend "\nI wasn't able to feel pain. My heart continues to pump, as if to replenish all the lost blood, {w}{nw}"


translate English day5_5540578b:


    extend "\nhot inside me, as my brain grows just as hot, as though it will melt."


translate English day5_76b2fe88_2:


    nvl clear


translate English day5_76b2fe88_3:


    nvl clear


translate English day5_290dbb2d:


    br "\n The heat filling the room makes my eyes go vacant. {w}{nw}"


translate English day5_f1f1f401:


    extend "\nBut this body of mine is still too heavy to dedicate to her in its entirety. {w}{nw}"


translate English day5_96817d27:


    extend "\nMy clouded vision rapidly darkens. I open my eyes, and the angel is still before me. {w}{nw}"


translate English day5_aafdca3c:


    extend "\nThe light permeates my mind. Even closing my eyes doesn't shut it out. It continues to glow brilliantly inside me."


translate English day5_4006ca6a:


    br "\n Today's dream is a little different than usual, for some reason. {w}{nw}"


translate English day5_0ba1022c:


    extend "\nAs always, the space I'm in is filled with dripping, festering, fetid entrails. But I'm not the one standing atop the pile of corpses this time. {w}{nw}"


translate English day5_30cac245:


    extend "I think someone else is standing there, but after a moment, they become yet another one of the countless dead bodies. {w}{nw}"


translate English day5_209c0766:


    extend "Sticky bubbles rise in a regular pattern from a hole made of water droplets.{w} I watch as it happens from afar."


translate English day5_a88eb16d:



    nvl clear
    br "\n I look around, but see nothing but rotting flesh.{w} There's not a living person in sight.{w} Where did they all go?{w} Why am I standing here alone?{w}{nw}"


translate English day5_8d9ab69c:


    extend "\n I can't come up with an answer.{w} I've grown very tired of being in this situation. {w}{nw}"


translate English day5_6fa710af:


    extend "I just stand there, staring at the bright-red ground.{w} Then, I slowly approach the body closest to me.{w} The pool of blood has a sour stench to it. {w}{nw}"


translate English day5_fb20d8d2:


    extend "I think I see the corpse move, ever so slightly. I narrow my eyes to focus my vision and get a little closer. {w}{nw}"


translate English day5_38dac30d:


    extend "I want to see the face."


translate English day5_99be970f:



    nvl clear
    br "\n But a moment later, something hard to accept occurs before my eyes.{w} The stomach of the corpse I thought moved begins to expand. {w}{nw}"


translate English day5_384f3394:


    extend "Is it because of the rain? The body's gut expands like a frog's vocal sac, then eventually, it bursts. {w}{nw}"


translate English day5_9aaae3fa:


    extend "I try to gasp, but I can't.{w} My face, my head, my chest--they've all been splattered with the filth from that stomach. {w}{nw}"


translate English day5_f3c59a5a:


    extend "\nA wet, dripping clump of something falls out of my damp bangs and blocks my vision, causing me to scream.{w} I kick off the slippery ground and begin to run. {w}{nw}"


translate English day5_091f0cb2:


    extend "\nMy eyes move quickly, searching for someone.{w} The angel. {w}The angel hasn't come yet."


translate English day5_835f3586:



    nvl clear
    br "\n I bring my hands up in front of me, clasped together as if in prayer.{w} I pray, from the bottom of my heart, for that angel to arrive.{w} Because as long as she doesn't, I will never wake from this dream. {w}{nw}"


translate English day5_bbd575fc:


    extend "\nThe sky is still dark, without a single ray of light in sight.{w} I pray over and over for her to get here and end this terrifying nightmare. {w}{nw}"


translate English day5_50fceda2:


    extend "\nI search for the angel of my own volition."


translate English day5_76b2fe88_4:


    nvl clear


translate English day5_1b930b6f:


    br "\n As though it's always been something that can only be given to those who pray, the dark skies that I thought would remain closed forever finally part in twain, and from them shines an overflowing, brilliant light that makes me open my eyes wide. {w}{nw}"


translate English day5_da796207:


    extend "\nShe has appeared.{w} The angel spreads her immaculate wings, bearing blinding light behind her, and places her slender arms around me. {w}{nw}"


translate English day5_d12f5c3b:


    extend "\nI am sure that she is beautiful, the very essence of purity--but the rotten stench of this place is too ubiquitous, and it gets in the way of that beauty. {w}{nw}"


translate English day5_a05c3e55:


    extend "\nMy back, which is up against a slick wall, itches all over, as though hundreds of small insects are crawling around on it. {w}{nw}"


translate English day5_a6ce91f3:


    extend "\nI pull myself off of the wall, and right in front of me is the angel.{w} I am sure that her warmth is something I have avoided for a very long time, and which I now continue to seek out. {w}{nw}"


translate English day5_a45b2e53:


    extend "\nAn instinctive distress gnaws at my mind."


translate English day5_76b2fe88_5:


    nvl clear


translate English day5_76b2fe88_6:


    nvl clear


translate English day5_e908fe44:


    br "\n She is an angel.{w} A being so far beyond me that I shouldn't even be able to lock eyes with her, much less touch her. {w}{nw}"


translate English day5_6f21d60d:


    extend "\nAnd now, her pure hands stroke my body. {w}{nw}"


translate English day5_15eedebf:


    extend "\nWho are you? Why do you have her face?{w} She sighs sweetly and light strong enough to rattle my brain blinds my eyes. {w}{nw}"


translate English day5_ecfd2c6f:


    extend "\nUnable to resist the urge to vomit welling up within me, I vomit out the smooth contents of my stomach.{w} The filth that sprung from me sullies her beautiful clothes, {w}{nw}"


translate English day5_c849ce73:


    extend "and it sticks to her hair, creating a miserable sight indeed.{w} But her smile remains unsullied and she does not withdraw the hand she held out to me."


translate English day5_76b2fe88_7:


    nvl clear


translate English day5_5bbe93a1:


    br "\n Ah! To think she would embrace me, dirty as I am, without a hint of cruelty...{w} What compassion she must possess. {w}{nw}"


translate English day5_d74b65c6:


    extend "\nI reverentially put my trembling hands around her back.{w} I accept her.{w} I embrace her, as she did me. {w}{nw}"


translate English day5_88018c9d:


    extend "\n\"It'll be alright.\" Her gentle fingertips stroke my head.{w} Her voice is so soft it's almost cruel.{w} She accepts me, wholeheartedly. {w}{nw}"


translate English day5_f55eb006:


    extend "\nIf I could remain like this with her for the rest of time, I would gladly offer her everything.{w} This warmth, the heavy beating of my heart. {w}{nw}"


translate English day5_935d19cc:


    extend "\nThe sense of being engulfed."


translate English day5_8bd50912:



    nvl clear
    "\n It's morning.{w} As soon as I open my eyes, I bring my trembling hands up in front of me."


translate English day5_1baa06a4:


    "They're sweaty, as though I've been clenching them for a long time.{w} I somehow feel like I'm still wandering in a dream.{w} In the dimly lit room, I see the scarlet-colored inner wall through my fingers."


translate English day5_c1a0eac9:


    et "It's probably because of what happened last night."


translate English day5_30c04b23:



    nvl clear
    "\n My memories of the past few days' events begin to mix themselves into my thoughts, and I have to shake my head firmly several times to get ahold of myself."


translate English day5_f21884f5:


    "The air blowing into my clothes is cold, so I go under my blanket.{w} What time is it?{w} Voices of a crowd of people assault my ears."


translate English day5_685481d5:


    "But something isn't right.{w} I cover my ears, but the noise won't stop."


translate English day5_e4355c4d:


    et "The voices grate on my nerves whether I like it or not, giving me a stinging headache."


translate English day5_ce7f99a4:



    nvl clear
    "\n I stay under the covers for a little while longer.{w} My headache is causing me to hear things that aren't there."


translate English day5_114b72a2:


    "My body is so cold, but my dizzy head is so uncomfortably warm. I can't seem to focus my eyes, either.{w} Still, I swing my lifeless legs over the side of the bed and get up."


translate English day5_bc8e20ab:


    et "For once, I can't stand being alone."


translate English day5_3195b2cd:


    nar "The mood in the office feels weird.{w} It's unusually quiet, but the strange air about makes it feel like something's afoot."


translate English day5_d07fb975:


    nar "The excitement over seeing the blood of someone we know must not have abated yet."


translate English day5_e6c58e6e:


    nar "Despite the job of everyone here being to clean up corpses, they're fascinated by incidents of strangling."


translate English day5_73be292f:


    nar "Everyone dies one day.{w} It's an obvious fact, but the people here seem to completely forget that occasionally."


translate English day5_30594105:


    nar "That must be why they're this happy--and afraid."


translate English day5_669bb0bf:


    nar "......"


translate English day5_aea05158:


    nar "The incident continues in my mind. I recall the girl's face."


translate English day5_6e5aff70:


    nar "Her usual confident smile was warped into a terribly twisted expression; her black, manicured nails were split;"


translate English day5_c7ee04ad:


    nar "and the heavy scent of sweat-soaked skin changed to the stench of burning as the brand pressed against her.{w} Suddenly, I feel like throwing up for no reason."


translate English day5_0f7a6025:


    my "Ah, good morning, [na2]. You're early today..."


translate English day5_97ae26d9:


    pl "Yeah... Right.{w} Well, I can't be late every day, can I?"


translate English day5_2f5de8ff:


    nar "I didn't feel like being in that room because of the nightmare this morning."


translate English day5_504429fe:


    nar "I can still feel the warmth of the woman in the dream.{w} Her soft hands, her gentle voice."


translate English day5_30e3a731:


    nar "As the last glow of the dream fades away into bitter reality, it makes me feel so much emptier."


translate English day5_6594a705:


    nar "Being alone is driving me crazy.{w} But I can't tell Maya any of this."


translate English day5_0ae83791:


    nar "I carefully avert my gaze and look for something to talk about."


translate English day5_bc46bcd0:


    pl "...Alone today?"


translate English day5_86adb095:


    my "No... Not exactly. Over there..."


translate English day5_5af62ecd:


    nar "Maya's voice grows oddly quiet.{w} I turn the way she's looking and see a short-haired girl sitting."


translate English day5_f442994c:


    nar "Unlike usual, her shoulders were slumped, and she looked thinner for some reason."


translate English day5_c1d6587d:


    nar "A lot of people whispered to one another as they passed by her, but she ignored all of the stares and chatter."


translate English day5_346b526b:


    nar "From a glance at her eyes, I could tell she was crushed."


translate English day5_cd02583f:


    nar "Maya and I exchanged uncomfortable glances."


translate English day5_7e7e778a:


    pl "R-Right. They were always together..."


translate English day5_c5461292:


    nar "Though that senior member didn't seem to think so."


translate English day5_c721fd2b:


    pl "...Are you doing okay, Maya?"


translate English day5_23af1d56:


    my "A-Ah, I'm... I'm fine, but... I'm just worried about my sister is all..."


translate English day5_7cc668d9:


    pl "She'll be alright.{w} She's a strong person. A little bit of rest and she'll be back to her usual self."


translate English day5_db538918:


    my "I hope so..."


translate English day5_80998a82:


    nar "Maya then looks at my face and falls silent. She must be worried about me."


translate English day5_d4a33e04:


    nar "But she doesn't say anything else--probably because she saw what happened yesterday."


translate English day5_d113e981:


    nar "Maya's being considerate, because she knows how awkward it is."


translate English day5_070534c8:


    nar "She's such a kind person.{w} But it also makes me feel uneasy. Just how far ahead does Maya think?"


translate English day5_7c5b482f:


    hk "Good morning everyone!~"


translate English day5_ba3fdc8e:


    nar "Thankfully, the bishop arrives, cutting our brief and very awkward conversation short."


translate English day5_a3465eae:


    nar "She passes by us with a greeting, and for just a moment, her eyes flick over to me."


translate English day5_24d78a2c:


    nar "I could have just imagined it, but that look gave me goosebumps.{w} I avoid looking at her and take my seat.{w} A heavy sigh escapes me."


translate English day5_5da8b1f4:


    nar "Up close, the sight of the freckled girl was nothing like what I imagined."


translate English day5_69119f79:


    nar "Her dried-out lips, specked with a blood clot or two, quiver madly, and her cheeks are so sunken in you'd think she'd been starving for days."


translate English day5_346f7e55:


    nar "I say hello, but as I thought, she doesn't respond.{w} She's not ignoring me--it's more like she didn't hear anything at all."


translate English day5_06ddb94c:


    hk "Something very unfortunate happened yesterday.{w} That said, I hope you will all be able to focus on the day's work."


translate English day5_313b59f0:


    nar "The bishop politely consoles us over the loss of a member, even though the best thing to do in this situation would be to not mention the passing at all."


translate English day5_977e2ea2:


    nar "Every time I spot someone holding their breath and grinning in this dismal mood, it rattles me.{w} Are they scorning her death?"


translate English day5_13d4ab9a:


    nar "Or do they find the sexual implication of the immaculate bishop's words darkly comedic?"


translate English day5_fccfd4c8:


    nar "She is an empty husk, sitting there without moving an inch. Maya can't fully hide her distress."


translate English day5_c92263ce:


    pl "Hey... You doing alright?"


translate English day5_c9556fde:


    nar "In Maya's place, I try talking to her several times, and finally, she turns her head to me.{w} Her eyes are horrifically dark."


translate English day5_a78e5706:


    lz1 "Can you see it...? Over there?"


translate English day5_ac68adf6:


    nar "Her voice is hoarse as she points at a spot ahead of her.{w} Naturally, nothing is there."


translate English day5_2fdc09d6:


    pl "I don't see anything..."


translate English day5_2c5e32f6:


    nar "After I reply, she repeats those words, in a quiet voice."


translate English day5_ea267b93:


    lz1 "Can you see it over there?"


translate English day5_da531fec:


    nar "The same question.{w} This time, I don't respond."


translate English day5_1bb8a0f6:


    nar "But her finger still stays up, pointing in the direction she's facing.{w} Scared of what that could mean, I end up giving her the same answer as before."


translate English day5_3d505ce4:


    pl "Still don't see anything..."


translate English day5_6d5bd612:


    lz1 "Oh? I see..."


translate English day5_10fda1a3:


    nar "And then she falls quiet again.{w} Maya's expression is hopeless. She trembles, eventually looking like she's holding back tears."


translate English day5_dbfa0289:


    my "Please talk to us..."


translate English day5_fa8f50d5:


    nar "Her voice is trembling, too.{w} But the girl doesn't answer--doesn't even look at her--so Maya gets up and puts a hand on her shoulder."


translate English day5_2851796a:


    my "Hello...?{w} Please... Please answer me!"


translate English day5_d06e1980:


    nar "The girl simply lets her younger sister's hand jostle her. She looks like a straw doll."


translate English day5_2e1bc471:


    nar "Just as I start to feel really sorry for her, a hand slams down on the desk, which was dejectedly rattling along with her shell of a body."


translate English day5_a4e3bfa2:


    nar "It's Securett."


translate English day5_3334fc23:


    my "......"


translate English day5_05650b0e:


    nar "In her surprise, Maya releases her hand, and the girl raises her gaze to look at him.{w} Securett's sharp eyes stare down at her."


translate English day5_38aab911:


    sc "The bishop is calling for you."


translate English day5_7bae15a9:


    nar "Surprisingly aware, the girl stays still for a moment, then slowly gets herself up."


translate English day5_2708f156:


    nar "Her gait unsteady, she heads off toward the bishop's office.{w} We watch her wobble away in silence for a few moments."


translate English day5_1c2cbc89:


    sc "...Didn't think she'd be coming in today."


translate English day5_eb1e660c:


    pl "......"


translate English day5_137e07b6:


    nar "Securett quietly averts his gaze and looks at me."


translate English day5_f4ea3941:


    nar "Once again, he doesn't avoid my gaze. He confronts me, and even speaks to me.{w} I purposely don't answer him."


translate English day5_e7e65106:


    my "Umm... Cue, is she..."


translate English day5_c962e9d8:


    sc "Your sister will probably be leaving the temple and returning home."


translate English day5_eb853942:


    sc "...That is, if she even can.{w} You two are Erbets, aren't you?"


translate English day5_0fd5ef89:


    nar "Maya's eyes widen in surprise at hearing that."


translate English day5_c921c329:


    nar "I don't need to know what that means to instantly know it was a rude remark."


translate English day5_6ca548f7:


    pl "You're even acting nasty to Maya now?"


translate English day5_7d8ee735:


    sc "No, I'm trying to discuss something important."


translate English day5_0886ee1f:


    sc "Maya Erbet, I've been watching you for a while now and I have to say, your job performance is the *worst* I've ever seen."


translate English day5_abf69f8c:


    sc "If you don't shape up, you're not going to survive here--mark my words."


translate English day5_db5369a4:


    sc "Prolonging matters will only hurt you.{w} Maybe you should return with her today."


translate English day5_16d6f048:


    nar "His words are like a deadly dagger descending on Maya.{w} I almost raise a hand against him, but manage to control myself."


translate English day5_4432e2e1:


    nar "Not only does he want to insult me, he even wants to take Maya away from me?"


translate English day5_34b0413e:


    sc "But... If you still want to stay here a long time, then get ready, quickly. I have things to do today, too."


translate English day5_d179ee4f:


    pl "Wait, it's not like we need to force her to come.{w} And anyway, you're too busy to be showing that kind of consideration to a newcomer, aren't you?"


translate English day5_f349121f:


    pl "It's already day five. The two of us are enough to handle the usual jobs."


translate English day5_44efc26f:


    nar "The uncomfortable mood grows heavy, then completely comes to a halt.{w} Securett stops moving and gives me a look."


translate English day5_9dce617c:


    nar "He seems to want to say something to me, and I share the sentiment.{w} I'm not backing down."


translate English day5_cf67b20b:


    sc "Sigh... What are you talking about? It's not \"already\" day five--it's \"ONLY\" day five.{w} Nobody knows what could happen."


translate English day5_5deffbb6:


    sc "You still don't seem to get that the temple isn't a daycare. If you bungle something because you're alone, you'll just make more trouble for the rest of us."


translate English day5_1e31dea2:


    sc "Or wait?{w} Are you saying you're good enough not to let that happen?"


translate English day5_972fc556:


    sc "Please, just search the few brain cells you have in there. I'm sure you'll come up with the correct answer."


translate English day5_79767d00:


    pl "Could you shut that rude mouth of yours for two seconds?"


translate English day5_a70d1a6d:


    pl "There's a limit to how much you can treat others like they're idiots. I'm sick and tired of sucking up to your bad attitude."


translate English day5_4d411937:


    pl "Do you really not get it?{w} That nonsense you spew really, really aggravates me whenever you're around."


translate English day5_afca48aa:


    pl "All you do all day is bitch about every single thing.{w} It's no wonder nobody wants to talk to you."


translate English day5_bb3c18c9:


    pl "Maybe you could use a few lessons in friendliness before you learn how to dispose of corpses."


translate English day5_a460d66a:


    nar "I try to pick my words carefully, but I can't seem to quite come up with the right ones."


translate English day5_c0833b47:


    nar "His eyes are as cold as the air between us. I look into them dead-on."


translate English day5_c6984b9d:


    nar "With all the stuff that's happened, I really don't feel like working with him today."


translate English day5_77791284:


    sc "......"


translate English day5_9f1dfae0:


    my "...I'm...{cps=*0.1}so...{/cps}sorry..."


translate English day5_3de34fc1:


    my "I'm really sorry. I... I-I..."


translate English day5_77791284_1:


    sc "......"


translate English day5_c2421e1b:


    sc "You're venting to me, then?"


translate English day5_8c35f4ec:


    pl "...What?"


translate English day5_86cd5ada:


    sc "Yeah, I know exactly what you're trying to say."


translate English day5_f60b7929:


    nar "He glances between Maya and me for a second, then looks away."


translate English day5_d79c67af:


    nar "I had privately wondered how he'd react when he heard all that,"


translate English day5_c6e0c027:


    nar "but there's no anger in his expression at all.{w} It doesn't look like he's shocked though, either."


translate English day5_599cbee0:


    nar "He's probably known about his flaw for a long time, and honestly, that just makes me even more annoyed."


translate English day5_43dad6aa:


    sc "Do what you will."


translate English day5_0719ab79:


    nar "With those cold, curt words, he goes outside. I glare at him all the while."


translate English day5_0b54f081:


    my "[na2], are you angry...?"


translate English day5_7d07e4a5:


    pl "Sorry, Maya..."


translate English day5_19e7e395:


    pl "No, I'm not angry.{w} I just don't want to let him say those terrible things to you."


translate English day5_3334fc23_1:


    my "......"


translate English day5_242e9300:


    nar "Maya had to be the one feeling the most down of all, caught in between Securett and me.{w} I feel bad for making her feel that way."


translate English day5_9829133d:


    nar "But I don't think I misspoke.{w} On any other day, I might have handled him without breaking a sweat."


translate English day5_5714be02:


    nar "But today, I'm confident enough to stand up for what I said."


translate English day5_d52ee494:


    nar "I've learned things very quickly ever since I was little. I've already done work alone with Maya, too, when we were the only ones available."


translate English day5_019635af:


    nar "I collect myself and look at her. Fortunately, I don't see any tears yet.{w} It seems more like she's dealing with a mountain of anxiety."


translate English day5_ca1d69e3:


    pl "Maya, you're coming with, right?"


translate English day5_c0b71958:


    nar "Because of that, she hesitates to answer my question. Then again, she's never had much confidence."


translate English day5_32b654bc:


    nar "If she's angry, I can't tell at who. Me? I can't say for sure she's not mad at me."


translate English day5_e9b723ed:


    nar "So she's at even more of a loss now.{w} Did he say those things knowing all that?"


translate English day5_a297ff67:


    nar "Well, I'm the only one who knows her deep down at this point.{w} I can help her in ways nobody else can."


translate English day5_522c246c:


    nar "A while passes without an answer, so I say her name again."


translate English day5_0dcdbbd7:


    pl "Maya?"


translate English day5_9f65045b:


    my "I... I don't know.{w} Securett is right. I'm bad at my job, so I'm honestly just dead weight in this department..."


translate English day5_5a69de8f:


    my "I don't want to drag you down with me, too, [na2]..."


translate English day5_46142c8f:


    pl "You're not dragging anyone down. Seriously, just ignore what that guy said!"


translate English day5_8121171a:


    pl "I've been with you this whole time. I know you've been trying harder than anyone."


translate English day5_081d886b:


    pl "It's not just him. That brand of unpleasantness comes with the job. You can't let yourself wither every time you hear it."


translate English day5_958d0392:


    my "...Do you really think so?"


translate English day5_1f965c69:


    pl "Of course I do! Like I said before, I'm on your side.{w} And if we do a good job today, that'll shut him right up!"


translate English day5_8776e510:


    my "Okay...{w} Thanks, [na2]."


translate English day5_a6e89620:


    nar "I privately breathe a sigh of relief at finally getting a yes from her."


translate English day5_9d26d52a:


    nar "I just hope that put a little pep in her step."


translate English day5_89023bd8:


    nar "Unlike most days, the documents and their folders are split up.{w} Did someone find it too annoying to sort every single sheet and file?"


translate English day5_54796754:


    nar "I pick up two papers set there evenly and examine their contents. I've gotten pretty used to reading addresses and seemingly random strings of numbers by now."


translate English day5_51eac735:


    nar "The letter here represents the type of job, and the number, its difficulty."


translate English day5_509e44b8:


    nar "When it comes to cleaning, for example, the difficulty is determine by how much the body has decayed. Apparently, this normally goes from 1 to 5."


translate English day5_1355b3ba:


    nar "The letters on these stand for cleaning and sterilization respectively, with numbers going from 2 to 4. That level of job shouldn't pose any issues."


translate English day5_76b2fe88_8:


    nvl clear


translate English day5_d68b0f20:


    "\n As expected, the work resolves without much trouble."


translate English day5_e02ef20b:


    "If Maya's slow at working, all I have to do is divide up the work properly.{w} And it had been a while since I worked this hard on something."


translate English day5_fa3d3653:


    "We would both grimace whenever we saw the remains of a bird or a cat stuck to the floor, but I didn't feel as much of a sense of disgust and rejection with the human bodies."


translate English day5_f4011129:


    "Until now, I'd figured people would leave their names behind them--or at least personal effects--but that was a grave misunderstanding."


translate English day5_506bea0b:


    et "When a person dies, they leave behind sticky excrement, urine, and fat.{w} When I took off the discolored blanket resting on this one, maggots and other bugs I don't know the name of came swarming out."


translate English day5_970eab2a:



    nvl clear
    "\n Particularly bad was the bathroom--when we looked at the small tub, it was spattered with dun-colored fluids."


translate English day5_1d0177f1:


    "It was impossible to tell, given the state of things, whether the body had been moved to a different place or if it had long since dissolved."


translate English day5_9bdd41b4:


    "As soon as I saw it, I got Maya to leave the bathroom, then threw up."


translate English day5_fb219383:


    "The already-present awful stench mixed with the raw, sour odor of my vomit, throwing my mind into further chaos."


translate English day5_ed9f1a60:


    et "But eventually--and reluctantly--I moved the body out of there."


translate English day5_8325b41d:



    nvl clear
    "\n I hated it, obviously, and I still don't remember what even gave me the mental strength to do it.{w} Maybe I could only do it because of how bewildered I was."


translate English day5_c2735b3b:


    "By-products like nails, hairs, and skin drifted in the filthy bubbles along with the contents of my stomach. As I watched the water and drugs float around, I remembered Maya was on the other side of the door."


translate English day5_12f6ff20:


    et "And then Securett's words from this morning came back to me.{w} I'd wanted so badly to deny them, but I couldn't--I must have been too exhausted."


translate English day5_1b22a5ef:


    pl "I guess that does it for today. That took a little longer than expected."


translate English day5_3c96b27b:


    my "I'm sorry I kept getting in the way..."


translate English day5_e0b91cf4:


    pl "Hrm? Oh..."


translate English day5_899ca8fa:


    nar "I can't actually manage to say anything authentic--probably because of the exhaustion.{w} You idiot. Just deny it and move on! What are you doing?!"


translate English day5_3c5d2ecf:


    nar "Quickly, I look at Maya's face and search for another topic of conversation, but I can't seem to come up with one."


translate English day5_1b546db5:


    nar "My eyes are tired. I feel like I lost sleep this morning because of that weird dream.{w} Meanwhile, Maya's face grows darker and darker as I look at her."


translate English day5_663b077b:


    nar "Does she see exhaustion when she looks at me? Do I look like I'm pushing myself?{w} If she does..."


translate English day5_84f5b871:


    nar "I stop thinking about it.{w} I know it's a slim chance, but I'm scared she'll turn my own words back around on me."


translate English day5_2697d390:


    pl "That was more work than we usually have! I wonder if every day will be like this once we're officially priests."


translate English day5_bd3981ad:


    my "I... I suppose.{w} This is already our fifth day, after all..."


translate English day5_6e70fa4b:


    pl "Went by in a flash, huh?"


translate English day5_79e43512:


    my "Do you really think so? I'm actually surprised at how long every day seems to take..."


translate English day5_95766393:


    pl "I guess when I'm with you, the whole day goes by pretty quickly.{w} Like I haven't gotten enough, honestly."


translate English day5_91168c42:


    my "Geez..."


translate English day5_63f061bb:


    nar "On our way back, I notice that the air around us is starting to feel strange."


translate English day5_7d792476:


    nar "Maya draws back a step. Her frightened gaze lands on some decayed grass and trees.{w} Until this morning, this road was an overgrown forest path."


translate English day5_294306e7:


    nar "The earth is rotting.{w} I already know what that means. Is this another way the Pestis field expands?"


translate English day5_f56e93c3:


    my "We can't use this path anymore..."


translate English day5_c752c8b3:


    pl "Let's go around from the other side."


translate English day5_e08cd77d:


    my "But we've never been on that path before..."


translate English day5_99337c8a:


    pl "Hey, if it gets us where we're going, it's just another path back, right? It'll just be a bit longer of a walk than normal!"


translate English day5_76b2fe88_9:


    nvl clear


translate English day5_f07b2650:


    nar "We walk for a pretty long time.{w} Avoiding the invisible Pestis field is really tough--we don't know exactly how far it has spread."


translate English day5_299f4363:


    nar "The fear of the unknown hurries us along and the sense that we're taking a very long detour triggers both unease and relief in us."


translate English day5_f265a4a4:


    nar "Eventually, we come to a secret passage.{w} The ceiling is dark and the ground is soggy."


translate English day5_bc851563:


    nar "From afar, I figured the darkness was caused by all the big trees nearby, but now that we're here, it turns out we're in some kind of old building."


translate English day5_72776868:


    pl "We've been walking for a while. How are you holding up?"


translate English day5_bc79ad6e:


    my "I'm still okay..."


translate English day5_2798766d:


    my "I wonder what time it is.{w} I can never tell here..."


translate English day5_ee8d6915:


    pl "Ha, you're telling me!"


translate English day5_04589b97:


    nar "During the midnight sun, you can't even tell if it's day or night, much less what time it is."


translate English day5_6def5752:


    nar "I'm accustomed to walking under the hot sun now, but it not rising or setting at all is hard for me to get used to."


translate English day5_1ce0ea54:


    nar "The sky may be quiet, but the events that transpire beneath it certainly aren't. Things that would normally happen at night"


translate English day5_e2dfb078:


    nar "frequently occur even during the day, muddying the border between day and night, causing those who sleep into the day to lose track of the time. That's what's happening to me right now."


translate English day5_12f64b3f:


    nar "The sun never goes away in this white night."


translate English day5_30dd651c:


    nar "The eternal sun makes it feel like we're living through a single never-ending day. It makes it hard for me to breathe and dulls the senses."


translate English day5_81cb34a7:


    nar "During the polar night, you can't even tell if it's day or night, much less what time it is."


translate English day5_3cdf93da:


    nar "I'm accustomed to walking under the hot sun now, but adapting to the polar night takes more than just letting your eyes get used to things."


translate English day5_edc0834e:


    nar "The sky may be quiet and asleep, but the events that transpire beneath it certainly aren't. Things that would normally happen at night"


translate English day5_f8e29993:


    nar "occur frequently even during the day, muddying the border between day and night, causing those who sleep into the day to lose track of the time. That's what's happening to me right now."


translate English day5_e0151d59:


    nar "The sun never rises in this polar night. The only light we ever get is the miniscule, momentary bit of blue illumination that appears whenever the date changes."


translate English day5_df1abed9:


    nar "The endless night is suffocating. It's blunted my senses."


translate English day5_08f9c6a3:


    nar "We walk for a very long time. The ground begins to feel closer to me--maybe because of the overwhelming exhaustion."


translate English day5_57a0509a:


    nar "The sky is low, hanging over us like a ceiling, crushing down on us."


translate English day5_6bc21476:


    nar "Sometimes I'll snap out of it and straighten my shoulders and back, but the more I walk, the more my body wants to slump over."


translate English day5_b0d42e7b:


    nar "It feels like I'm suffocating without even speaking, my body and mind both unable to get in a good breath of air. My breathing comes in and out of me in short bursts."


translate English day5_11269106:


    nar "I try to consciously force myself to breathe deeply, but there's not enough oxygen getting to my brain."


translate English day5_f5ba8613:


    nar "Gasping for breath all hunched over is kind of embarrassing, so I stop and take a deep breath."


translate English day5_6fa6fe8d:


    pl "Haaah..."


translate English day5_27f2674c:


    my "[na2], are you tired?"


translate English day5_bc9351b5:


    pl "I mean, we've walked pretty far, but... I'm fine. Nothing to worry about."


translate English day5_dc1c57e9:


    pl "Despite our... situation, it can't be that late. Not late enough to be worried over, anyway."


translate English day5_00405717:


    pl "Though I guess it's well past lunchtime by now."


translate English day5_d24e73cc:


    pl "But we're out now. Want to go buy something to eat?"


translate English day5_417f519a:


    my "No... I think I'm just going to go home.{w} I'm not particularly hungry and I don't have any money anyway."


translate English day5_6010aa49:


    pl "But you keep skipping meals, day after day. What if you collapse from hunger on a particularly tough job?"


translate English day5_f79caa85:


    my "I'll be okay. I doubt I would have been able to eat if we'd gotten back on time anyway.{w} A-And my mind is all messed up thinking about my sister..."


translate English day5_bf544e46:


    pl "Is what happened this morning still bothering you?"


translate English day5_2f242215:


    my "\"Bothering\" isn't really the right word...{w} I guess it's more like... I'm scared."


translate English day5_de73add6:


    pl "Scared?"


translate English day5_c9977d11:


    my "...You saw the Pestis before. That's scary, right?"


translate English day5_815d18ac:


    my "I've felt that way for a long time.{w} It's terrifying to think I can't see something that everyone else can."


translate English day5_ef494696:


    my "I wonder if Securett was able to see my sister's ghost..."


translate English day5_e70b0713:


    pl "...I really doubt that."


translate English day5_f22b461d:


    nar "With the magicians protecting the temple, ghosts wouldn't be able to get inside.{w} It's an obvious fact--and one Maya must know."


translate English day5_182d69f8:


    nar "I think she realizes that too."


translate English day5_65f53a0a:


    nar "Something that looks like it's right there, yet doesn't exist...{w} I, too, know what that something really is."


translate English day5_deac181a:


    nar "As I remember my morning headache, my pace gradually slows.{w} At first, Maya walks quietly beside me, then after some time, she finally nods in response."


translate English day5_b1649efe:


    my "I guess I can't go home anymore, can I..."


translate English day5_31167d30:


    nar "She says it almost like a self-imposed question."


translate English day5_07270f8e:


    nar "A discussion she's having with her--one that I can't give an answer to.{w} I just wish I could get my thoughts in order a little more."


translate English day5_4ad4ed37:


    nar "Maybe not going home was a form of giving up for her.{w} Deep down, I really hope she doesn't."


translate English day5_96959016:


    nar "I feel happy when I think about being with Maya more."


translate English day5_9bd48afb:


    nar "A reliable family and understanding friends.{w} Unchanging days in a stable lifestyle."


translate English day5_37c0796f:


    nar "Being surrounded by things like those only narrows your outlook on life."


translate English day5_88007532:


    nar "The world is so vast, and there are so many things to do.{w} Opportunities come to those who work for them.{w} I don't think she'd benefit from sticking around in a cramped little nest like this."


translate English day5_4c2a7682:


    nar "As I try to get some words out of my currently sluggish mind, I notice something odd in our path. I move myself in front of Maya."


translate English day5_a1dcc7d2:


    nar "Something's moving in the dark.{w} I'm not sure why I didn't notice this earlier. Maybe a day of climbing corpses has dulled my sense of smell."


translate English day5_32dcc70e:


    nar "But after perceiving it--whatever it was--I could keenly smell the rotten stench.{w} And for some reason, I felt accustomed to the noise, which was like feet scraping on the ground."


translate English day5_8bc7d10e:


    nar "It was hidden behind the roof, so I couldn't make it out clearly, but it definitely didn't look human."


translate English day5_3c3bf726:


    my "One of the Lost...?"


translate English day5_b4a27652:


    pl "But it should still be daytime... Is it here because of how dark the path is?"


translate English day5_ab1e72b3:


    nar "I remember hearing that some of the Lost occasionally wake up early.{w} We rush to retreat from it, but it's already spotted us."


translate English day5_a8d07842:


    nar "I hear Maya give a sharp shriek.{w} At the same time, the thing launches itself at me." with sshake


translate English day5_88cfee8d:



    nvl clear
    "\n The bag in my hand is knocked away, and my body hits the ground.{w} The ground beneath is still muddy; I whip out my arms and legs to make sure my back doesn't touch it."


translate English day5_75b9bdcd:


    "I'm not carrying a weapon, and the thing pushing on me is awfully strong.{w} Warning sirens blare in my mind, telling me that if I loosen up even a little, I'm a goner."


translate English day5_1e4bca9f:


    "Perhaps because of my low position, my waist trembles.{w} I bend one of my legs as far as it will go, then lash it at the thing's gut."


translate English day5_6fe66234:


    et "The hit that I land feels weaker than the power I put into it."


translate English day5_e99393b5:



    nvl clear
    "\n Possibly in response to being attacked, the Lost releases its hands from me and instead begins thrusting its arms at my eyeballs as if to gouge them out."


translate English day5_e2c9e277:


    "I put even more force into my leg for the next kick, which hits it square in the gut. Quickly, I follow up with a punch to its undefended jaw."


translate English day5_d188fa84:


    "And while my fist connects, I don't feel any of the bone or flesh I would from punching a human body."


translate English day5_b87df494:


    "Instead, something gooey, goopy, and cold touches my fist.{w} It's the thing's nasty tongue, which has been hanging out of its mouth this whole time, and what looks like a small tooth."


translate English day5_134ce64d:


    et "Still, grabbing its head was the right move.{w} My weight transfers onto it, easily toppling the beast."


translate English day5_91f5dd99:



    nvl clear
    "\n I desperately try to crush anything that I perceive as a part of the thing's body."


translate English day5_fe94c360:


    "\"Maya, there should be a grimoire in the tool sack!{w} Grab whatever looks useful, and--\""


translate English day5_faf55f4b:


    "\"I can't! I've never cast any spells before...!\""


translate English day5_7db2d590:


    et "\"You can! I know you can do this, Maya!\"" with sshake


translate English day5_5078b935:


    "Maya, frightened--her legs having apparently given out--crawls over to the bag and fishes through it.{w} If I can't keep Maya protected here..."


translate English day5_25e03364:


    "No. I don't want to think of that possibility."


translate English day5_e6dd0745:


    "I still can't believe we just happened to be on our own, just happened to take a huge detour to avoid the shifted Pestis field, and then just happened to run into an early-rising Lost."


translate English day5_5783ae7e:


    et "In fact, I don't believe it. This can't all be a string of mere coincidences."


translate English day5_184f5f42:



    nvl clear
    "\n This bad luck is too contrived to be anything but a trial.{w} Someone is watching over us.{w} I must protect Maya."


translate English day5_99b5eb33:


    "Maya begins to stammer something, her voice shaking.{w} Although I know I connected with a kick before and heard something tear, when I look again, I can see the wound rapidly healing."


translate English day5_6b0a46aa:


    "My pulse quickens as I see the thing up close.{w} Then I notice something strange."


translate English day5_2e825d00:


    "The thing pushing me with its knees and legs is slender, for some reason.{w} All I did was put my weight onto it, and soon I hear a hoarse shriek from below."


translate English day5_c543fb74:


    et "It's a woman.{w} A woman with coarse, disheveled hair that looks like straw."


translate English day5_76b2fe88_11:


    nvl clear


translate English day5_76b2fe88_10:


    nvl clear


translate English day5_53f0a6e4:


    "\n For a moment, I can't help but see someone else there.{w} I swallow my spit wrong and start coughing."


translate English day5_3399652e:


    "Maya is behind me right now, utterly frightened.{w} Still, she has faith in me."


translate English day5_4b674fba:


    "If I stop moving, it'll only make things worse for her."


translate English day5_7b005b1c:


    "To prevent that, I swing my fist.{w} My hand is shaking, but the stigmata I can see projected inside my glove is red."


translate English day5_1abf402f:


    et "This time, the Lost's wound doesn't heal.{w} Looks like my punch was super effective."


translate English day5_76b2fe88_12:


    nvl clear


translate English day5_36d319bf:


    "\n I continue to throw punches.{w} Maya's breath quickens, trembling, exhaling far too many times within a few seconds." with sshake


translate English day5_72621a7c:


    "Maya cries out; she doesn't know what to do.{w} The Lost screams in rage. It makes me lose control of my breathing as well."


translate English day5_dc6e5dd3:


    "I can't stop shaking--because of the fear, or perhaps the hopelessness surpassing it."


translate English day5_1975834c:


    "The Lost opens its protruding eyeballs wide and looks at me.{w} Its skin, cold and blue, is crushed along with its black, sticky blood."


translate English day5_2fcc388a:


    et "Its screaming little throat still moves, as though it's got a life of its own.{w} Its hand reaches for me, its fingers shriveled and its nails falling off."


translate English day5_76b2fe88_13:


    nvl clear


translate English day5_8c00f55f:


    "\n \"I did nothing wrong!!!\" it shrieks.{w} Her voice is much more vivid now and it rattles my brain."


translate English day5_534db5e9:


    "Then whose fault is it?{w} Are you trying to say I did something wrong?{w} No, that's not it. Nobody thinks that." with sshake


translate English day5_d0943f4a:


    "Each time that terrifying vision flashes before my eyes, I put more strength into my fist."


translate English day5_d7753ddb:


    "\"I'm scared! I'm scared...!\" says Maya desperately, as though clinging to something."


translate English day5_c0e16654:


    "The Lost isn't moving anymore.{w} Occasionally, a small ray of light shines on one of the shards of its soiled flesh."


translate English day5_16d25544:


    et "I'm out of breath. As I take in a deep inhale, I get dizzy."


translate English day5_76b2fe88_14:


    nvl clear


translate English day5_09481da4:


    nar "...I'm pretty sure we're supposed to remove the corpse's head in order to dispose of them safely."


translate English day5_d6b616c9:


    nar "When my brain make it that far, tears burst from my bloodshot eyes.{w} What the hell am I doing?"


translate English day5_3b5e735a:


    nar "I can't be doing something like this right now.{w} My body is limp, and I can't even lift up my head, much less the rest of me."


translate English day5_857a1e5a:


    nar "Every time I draw a breath, I hear a scratching sound inside my dry throat."


translate English day5_76b2fe88_15:


    nvl clear


translate English day5_eb613bd6:


    "\n A moment later, my whole body is assaulted by a sharp pain." with sshake


translate English day5_1fd9fbde:


    "The pain is explosive and intense, and my weary body instantly has strength again.{w} I scream, rolling on the mud-covered ground."


translate English day5_965a637c:


    "My arms burn as though someone set fire to them. The pain is concentrated on one spot."


translate English day5_6b35a2af:


    "My bandages are loose, and from inside, I can see that my arms are dark red."


translate English day5_0ba6aad4:


    "I get the raw, fresh stench of iron--the blood present hasn't been pooling there for a long time, nor has the skin been decaying.{w} The fact that it's flowing from me whips my mind into a frenzy."


translate English day5_082e0161:


    "Maya continues to say she's scared, she scared,{w} she's so scared.{w} So, so, so scared."


translate English day5_76b2fe88_16:


    nvl clear


translate English day5_e7f76d9c:


    "\n I've inhaled enough of the odor of a dead body burning to make me sick. Normally, at this point, {w} the villagers set fire to the big pile of straw, then go around that night drinking wine and eating food."


translate English day5_ea245104:


    "I'm seeing a vision of the funerals that I know from before.{w} That's what death has always been to me."


translate English day5_7bde9d77:


    et "But I was wrong.{w} Death is hot and it stinks to high heaven."


translate English day5_2138acbb:



    nvl clear
    "\n I feel as though I hear footsteps running to me from far away."


translate English day5_4507a3cd:


    "At first, there are gasps for breath, which then quiet as they judge the situation before them.{w} The words I hear next are hopeless ones."


translate English day5_e09d62b4:


    "I know I've heard this voice before, but for some reason, it sounds like someone I'm hearing for the first time."


translate English day5_4c67834c:


    "The voice calls my name many a time from very close to me.{w} Eventually, something covers my eyes--a heavy cloth, maybe."


translate English day5_e74249a6:


    "Their hands are busy, and their voice is strained."


translate English day5_66331ad2:


    "\"...through that way, it's the only short...\""


translate English day5_5c6a536b:


    "\"...really... I'm... sorry... I'm...\""


translate English day5_f1b35f1c:


    "\"...mustn't... remove the blindfold until... Please, calm down...\""


translate English day5_a52ceab3:


    et "The voices of the people moving about busily in front of me grow hazy in my ears."


translate English day5_7f676abc:



    nvl clear
    br2 "\n {color=000}It's an odd sight.{w} Many people stand in a line. The floor is painted with excrement, a strange juxtaposition with the otherwise beautiful place. {/color}{w}{nw}"


translate English day5_c6dac3b1:


    extend "\n {color=000}They look like people I know, but also like people I never knew. {/color}{w}{nw}"


translate English day5_5ce21703:


    extend "\n {color=000}My name is called. I am alone as I walk past the row of people and stand on top of a banister.{w} A bishop is there. {/color}{w}{nw}"


translate English day5_c44e2db9:


    extend "\n {color=000}I've never seen him before.{w} He holds his thumb, index finger, and middle finger up in front of me, as though he wants me to imitate him. {/color}{w}{nw}"


translate English day5_5c2e43f4:


    extend "\n {color=000}Awkwardly, I lift my hand and imitate him. He begins to speak slowly. {/color}"


translate English day5_941d4d23:



    nvl clear
    "{color=#000}{size=0}{k=0}Our lord, who art the source of the holy gospel and life itself, hear our prayer.{/k}{/size}{fast}{/color}{nw}"


translate English day5_11585940:


    br "\n Each of the people behind me recites those words. {w}{nw}"


translate English day5_f8b07d97:


    extend "\nBut some of the voices stammer and fumble the words, as though not everyone knows them. Honestly, I can barely tell what they're saying. {w}{nw}"


translate English day5_e82565a3:


    extend "\nI wonder what the looks on their faces are as they stand behind me.{w} And what face am I supposed to make for this person in front of me, whose expression I can't read? {w}{nw}"


translate English day5_189dd5a9:


    extend "\nA yellow light shines brilliantly before me, throwing my entire state of mind into disarray. {w}{nw}"


translate English day5_2ec745e7:


    extend "\nThe bishop lowers his hand, and his voice--which had been growing softer and softer--stops entirely.{w} Next, he calls the name of the next follower to stand atop the banister. {w}{nw}"


translate English day5_2d4fe618:


    extend "\nIt's her name--one that we all should consider sacred."


translate English day5_76b2fe88_17:


    nvl clear


translate English day5_fefafc7b:


    nar "The ceiling I see upon waking up is pure white.{w} I don't see any of the dark red creeping into my vision and making me dizzy."


translate English day5_22d8f84c:


    nar "I can't feel that seemingly endless pain anymore.{w} I blink twice, slowly, my mind still foggy."


translate English day5_00b127f9:


    nar "Then I turn my head and see Arnie, eyes closed, beside the bed.{w} She's sitting with her hands clasped on her lap."


translate English day5_594c1a1e:


    nar "Her black hair is the polar opposite of this dim, white infirmary, making her look even more like a foreign object here."


translate English day5_9fe98c88:


    nar "In a quiet voice, I call her name.{w} Right away, she opens her gentle eyes and smiles at me."


translate English day5_f2621fec:


    nar "Am I still in a dream?"


translate English day5_40b07bf4:


    ar "Ah. You've awoken."


translate English day5_f56dfdfd:


    pl "What are you doing here...?"


translate English day5_d600e496:


    ar "I was too worried not to come, hence, I have."


translate English day5_00b8f19e:


    gr "Yes, you gave everyone quite the fright."


translate English day5_3a9399b8:


    pl "If you're here, Doctor... Am I in the temple infirmary?"


translate English day5_6ea6fc3d:


    gr "Good morning, [na2].{w} You've been through quite a scary experience. Does it hurt anywhere?"


translate English day5_2d708d89:


    pl "How did I get here?"


translate English day5_cbcef004:


    pl "Maya! Is Maya alright?!" with sshake


translate English day5_49efa372:


    gr "I'm having her rest separately.{w} She's not injured, but she seems to be in shock."


translate English day5_7881d62a:


    gr "Take a breath, [na2]. She and you both need undisturbed bed rest for now."


translate English day5_d8abe781:


    pl "Thank goodness..."


translate English day5_c58d3f37:


    nar "Now that I know Maya is safe, my mind begins to clear."


translate English day5_2443bc3e:


    nar "Come to think of it, I hurt my arm, but the wound has disappeared without a trace, healed in its entirety."


translate English day5_9641e915:


    nar "That said, it's not exactly pretty, I suppose.{w} There's black markings where it healed over, like a boulder re-covered with moss."


translate English day5_38a09db4:


    nar "The doctor smiles uneasily as she watches me look at it. Then, her expression quickly hardens again."


translate English day5_949c35a4:


    gr "Arne, I have something important to talk to [na2] about.{w} I'm terribly sorry, but could you..."


translate English day5_14eaa4c9:


    ar "Oh, of course. Thank you for lending me your seat like this."


translate English day5_95145d24:


    ar "Brother [na2], be well."


translate English day5_4a25f82e:


    nar "With streamlined movements, Arnie leaves the room.{w} The doctor sits down in her place."


translate English day5_55af3c97:


    gr "I'm sorry for kicking your girlfriend out.{w} Disappointed?"


translate English day5_7d570f27:


    pl "Wha--No, we're not like...!"


translate English day5_97282855:


    nar "I trail off. Actually... What are Arnie and I, anyway?"


translate English day5_a6f3106e:


    nar "Normally, I never would have even met the princess of the Alternatas."


translate English day5_57715b60:


    nar "The only reason I can talk to her without interruption is because of our strange relationship--one where we're engaged to one another."


translate English day5_fc4ebb2e:


    nar "Until now, that would have been a totally unrealistic thing for me, something about other people, not me.{w} But every time I met her face to face, it got more real and real."


translate English day5_fe104467:


    gr "She's a good girl, you know.{w} She's been so busy lately, but she still came here right away and stayed here the whole time until you woke up."


translate English day5_67f4f0d0:


    pl "She did?"


translate English day5_15e64248:


    gr "Mm, she did!{w} If she were my daughter, I would be so proud of her!"


translate English day5_520ad110:


    gr "But it also saddens me a little, knowing that such a perfect girl can only come from a very strict family situation."


translate English day5_eb1e660c_1:


    pl "......"


translate English day5_d00f800e:


    nar "She turns away, lost in thought.{w} A silver band sparkles on her left ring finger."


translate English day5_5fb03643:


    gr "[na2], I don't know how you see things, but you mustn't make so much trouble for those worried about you."


translate English day5_4be7fc32:


    pl "It's not like I was doing it on purpose..."


translate English day5_45395f06:


    gr "That includes me."


translate English day5_344af3aa:


    pl "You were worried about me?"


translate English day5_e1481c9b:


    gr "Naturally!{w} Any boy who makes a woman wait is bound to turn into a no-good dog of a man."


translate English day5_126417ac:


    gr "For example..."


translate English day5_5f322971:


    nar "She lets herself trail off mischievously as a sheaf of papers is placed atop her head.{w} A man is standing behind her, a scowl on his face."


translate English day5_ff682c40:


    nar "I've seen him around pretty often.{w} While I know he's the bishop of the Health Department, this is my first time seeing him up close."


translate English day5_fafcaa21:


    "{nw}"


translate English day5_2d10d652:


    gr "My, my."


translate English day5_b26c71a1:


    qus "Your name was [na], correct?"


translate English day5_5bf71a1d:


    pl "Huh? Oh, uh, yeah."


translate English day5_aeb68c25:


    gg "I am {color=#93c47d}Gregor Cornish{/color}, bishop of the Health Department.{w} I very much regret having to trade introductions with you, given the state of things."


translate English day5_19c4e506:


    gg "Allow me to get down to business. What happened?"


translate English day5_8b26e822:


    gr "Please don't be too angry with him, Bishop..."


translate English day5_d8199def:


    gg "My anger will depend on his answer."


translate English day5_5cee954a:


    pl "...I mean, I didn't do anything wrong."


translate English day5_965078d5:


    pl "We had to take the long way around because of the Pestis, and then we ran into one of the Lost..."


translate English day5_6e91c9d9:


    gg "Is that Lost responsible for your arm's condition as well?"


translate English day5_85e6f328:


    pl "No, this just kinda happened all of a sudden. I'm not really sure why..."


translate English day5_cd735fae:


    pl "Speaking of which, I had borrowed a grimoire from the library..."


translate English day5_6fe9f9db:


    gg "The library?{w} They wouldn't allow anyone from the Cleanup Department in."


translate English day5_5198b2aa:


    pl "That's what I figured, but their bishop came to me personally, so..."


translate English day5_ff818662:


    gg "You mean the bishop of the Academics Department?"


translate English day5_0b8cdeb4:


    ev "It is a simple spell for increasing one's mana capacity, Bishop."


translate English day5_21da7f27:


    nar "An elegant voice strides into the fray.{w} In her hand, she carries the book in question."


translate English day5_b6d6ddde:


    gg "You again, Evelynn Violetta?"


translate English day5_4698ac49:


    nar "They probably know each other, given that they're both bishops.{w} Evelynn's only response to the man is a smile as she walks over to me."


translate English day5_7fe5314a:


    nar "The ticklish smell of her perfume hits me all at once."


translate English day5_6d6ebbb6:


    ev "I hope you are doing quite well, my handsome bed-bound gentleman."


translate English day5_854710f6:


    ev "It is often said that the children of man have incomprehensible fates.{w} You, however, seem to have encountered yours earlier than anticipated."


translate English day5_6bd662fa:


    pl "Man, you always show up out of nowhere and scare the crap out of me..."


translate English day5_661cb1f8:


    ev "Ah, your words give me great joy.{w} But, I am no more than an onlooker guided by the miracle you hath wrought."


translate English day5_ae90d1c5:


    pl "Miracle...?"


translate English day5_4cc8e488:


    nar "I make sure to look suspicious of her, but she doesn't answer.{w} Instead, she takes a seat on the edge of the bed."


translate English day5_3bf8de5c:


    nar "And then she looks me up and down, very carefully, until eventually her gaze comes to a stop.{w} I follow it and look at my arm again."


translate English day5_f013de07:


    nar "That was the right answer, apparently.{w} She smiles, though she keeps her eyes on it."


translate English day5_66dcd253:


    gg "Do you have any idea what you've done?"


translate English day5_510b0c28:


    ev "I'm afraid I don't.{w} Largely because I did not do it."


translate English day5_300d2b4d:


    ev "This matter is like a dream I never could have imagined.{w} Not with my hardened, unthinking brain."


translate English day5_1f349645:


    ev "The concept of increasing one's magic is akin to the concept of focus.{w} There is no creating power that simply does not exist."


translate English day5_845d0ccf:


    ev "All the more so because he has a mere two stigmata. His body should certainly be able to resist that level of power.{w} As I'm sure you're aware."


translate English day5_eb854be6:


    gg "......"


translate English day5_1bb9a84b:


    ev "I simply granted him the opportunity to learn from a newcomer to the Cleanup Department who had strayed from purity of heart."


translate English day5_868f4e26:


    ev "And according to her, she stopped part of the way through."


translate English day5_c5c00951:


    ev "The spell could very well be a factor, but in my opinion, it was not the root cause of this situation."


translate English day5_71da0a96:


    nar "She speaks slowly and without concern, but the man before us looks persistent, like he's not going to retreat from this."


translate English day5_fbbf33c2:


    nar "Although their eyes were now clashing in chaotic conflict, their discussion had been centered on me."


translate English day5_7c56a3c0:


    nar "And I couldn't even put in a word or two edgewise.{w} Looks like I'm starting to get really used to this situation."


translate English day5_255f8348:


    nar "This is probably how Maya felt this morning."


translate English day5_9c37d713:


    gr "[na2], is that wound on your arm from today?"


translate English day5_4b2082c0:


    pl "No, it's, uh, always been there.{w} It's from when I hurt my arm real bad when I was little."


translate English day5_b4b31b47:


    nar "I figured being casual would defuse the situation, but it seemed to ignite it even further.{w} The two ladies opened their eyes wide."


translate English day5_e55a24e9:


    nar "Under those covetous gazes, I felt a cold sweat break out along my spine.{w} I felt like prey before a hungry predator."


translate English day5_72cab8ec:


    nar "And when I looked more closely, it wasn't only the Academics Department bishop but Dr. Grette as well.{w} Although her expression was an anxious one, her eyes glittered with boldness."


translate English day5_e0cc5402:


    nar "Feeling the fear slowly rising, I turned to look at the Health Department bishop. He seemed to find this entire thing to be a serious headache."


translate English day5_f4fc945e:


    gg "...I don't understand."


translate English day5_805eb836:


    ev "The fact you don't mustn't frustrate you so.{w} All is the will of God. Some simply is not for the likes of humans to comprehend.{w} Isn't that right?"


translate English day5_449fbc04:


    gg "Evelynn..."


translate English day5_5d5e4406:


    nar "As before, she doesn't respond, instead rising from the bed to leave the room.{w} Before she does, she takes my hand and speaks to me."


translate English day5_69f8e5cd:


    nar "Her hand is strikingly beautiful and cold.{w} I can't sense anything human coming from it."


translate English day5_0317ded1:


    ev "Please, take good care of yourself and your power."


translate English day5_270d1331:


    ev "It would not be an exaggeration to say that to see you is akin to having an audience with God Himself..."


translate English day5_3776cdbb:


    nar "Dr. Grette watches as Bishop Evelynn leaves the room, then looks from her to Bishop Gregor, then at last, to me."


translate English day5_996a2fb0:


    nar "Her face is incredibly lonesome, as if she's worried about something. And she's been fidgeting, too. Perhaps she's as troubled by the whole situation as I am."


translate English day5_eafb82d4:


    gr "[na2], I'm sorry for all this--and right after you woke up, too. You probably didn't understand any of that."


translate English day5_fa74cdfd:


    gr "You can feel free to stay here, but... If you don't feel up to being here any longer, you're welcome to go back to your room."


translate English day5_afc683a9:


    gr "And if there's anything you need, feel free to tell me."


translate English day5_12231468:


    gg "Oh, and don't bother thinking about Evelynn Violetta's words too deeply, [na]."


translate English day5_4a35889c:


    gg "Her intelligence naturally surpasses all others at this temple, but to the same degree--"


translate English day5_a1b81d7a:


    pl "She's like a poet?"


translate English day5_1f1cdc63:


    gg "Hm... That is a fairly old way of insulting someone."


translate English day5_1742757d:


    gg "Essentially, your blood vessels are severely damaged.{w} We attempted to regenerate the wound using a spell, and we were able to stop the bleeding.{w} But don't think you've been fully healed just because there is no pain present."


translate English day5_89d4f691:


    gg "You were lucky this time. That's a fact, plain and simple.{w} Should a similar accident happen again, it's very likely you will lose the use of your arms permanently."


translate English day5_af61d657:


    pl "Permanently..."


translate English day5_93a7dc62:


    gr "Maybe you shouldn't have told him that right now..."


translate English day5_6b49074f:


    gg "All patients need a dose of the truth. The essence of healing is to face your own problems, after all."


translate English day5_56bcf1cd:


    gg "You'll need absolute rest and quiet."


translate English day5_b971462b:


    nar "The room falls quiet as the adults leave."


translate English day5_5e3d66e9:


    nar "I look at the ceiling idly, trying to gather my thoughts, but it doesn't work.{w} Everything was just so complicated."


translate English day5_33f1a362:


    nar "I can faintly smell disinfectant from my chilly blanket. These beds have been home to many patients."


translate English day5_65178b3b:


    nar "Assuming that thing used to be human, it was the first time I'd ever tried to punch someone that much. I could still find the marks of the impacts on my hands--and feel them all over my mind."


translate English day5_3ce665f1:


    nar "As I'm staring up at the ceiling, alone, someone enters the infirmary."


translate English day5_94bc1fc7:


    nar "It's Maya.{w} I nearly cry out in joy at seeing her face again, but when I see the person standing behind her, my expression freezes."


translate English day5_77791284_2:


    sc "......"


translate English day5_7bf56414:


    sc "...I changed my mind. I'm going back."


translate English day5_5a219560:


    my "W-Wait a minute, Cue...{w} Please don't leave..."


translate English day5_0404894a:


    nar "Maya grabs one of Securett's arms. He looks between the two of us, clearly troubled."


translate English day5_18a4dc69:


    nar "And when his eyes meet mine, he simply lowers his head and walks forward a few steps.{w} A short but uncomfortable silence follows."


translate English day5_8d05a025:


    sc "...How's the arm?"


translate English day5_beb92cb3:


    pl "Fine now. It doesn't hurt anymore."


translate English day5_22aa7300:


    sc "Oh..."


translate English day5_62c31660:


    nar "The conversation abruptly drops off into another awkward silence.{w} Unable to endure looking at him, I say something to Maya instead."


translate English day5_b0be8e5b:


    pl "How are you, Maya? You alright? Sorry for everything. That... must have been really scary."


translate English day5_8285dab0:


    my "I'm fine... Thanks to you, [na2]."


translate English day5_54f53a47:


    nar "But even as she answers me, she's keeping an eye on Securett's mood."


translate English day5_dfc9fcba:


    nar "He quickly notices Maya's staring, then raises his face up again."


translate English day5_7f24402b:


    sc "...I suppose that it's my fault."


translate English day5_75988d18:


    pl "Pff, you got that right! Nitpicking about everything, heh--"


translate English day5_3c1f413c:


    sc "I'm sorry. Truly."


translate English day5_6942dec2:


    nar "I was trying to play with him a little, but he gave such an earnest apology.{w} I definitely didn't expect that. His face is sheer white."


translate English day5_75773e21:


    nar "He's shaking. His embarrassment is actually confusing."


translate English day5_d83e86df:


    nar "After all, I figured he was gonna come in here and get angry at what I'd done. Wouldn't I, if things were reversed?"


translate English day5_4b40f376:


    sc "Neither of you have even finished your training yet, and yet I couldn't be a good teacher to you..."


translate English day5_afe14ff5:


    sc "Instead, I criticized you for a lot.{w} I'm... really, really sorry."


translate English day5_58e3a92d:


    pl "Wait, so way after saying all that stuff, now you're apologizing...? What are you getting at, Securett?"


translate English day5_df89f8d0:


    my "[na2]..."


translate English day5_242c6b01:


    sc "I don't expect easy forgiveness. I just--"


translate English day5_f670d578:


    pl "It's fine. I'm not an idiot. It's so easy to tell what an awkward guy like you is thinking."


translate English day5_87d92760:


    pl "You hated the thought of newbies like Maya and me messing up and getting hurt or even dying, didn't you?"


translate English day5_77791284_3:


    sc "......"


translate English day5_b117ed06:


    pl "But your \"strict teacher\" act didn't work out and a newbie returned injured in a way you never expected."


translate English day5_fefa440c:


    pl "And now you're the one being held responsible."


translate English day5_b9d83244:


    pl "Now you don't know what to do, so you come waltzing in with your head low, apologizing..."


translate English day5_2faf84c9:


    pl "I don't think I've ever seen anyone as awkward as you in my life, dude."


translate English day5_77791284_4:


    sc "......"


translate English day5_dd85eff5:


    nar "He doesn't respond. Securett just keeps his head down."


translate English day5_57f144fb:


    nar "Despite usually lecturing me from on high, he seems to be speechless. Maybe it's because I'm getting right to the point this time."


translate English day5_bf7e7350:


    nar "I've imagined him with this expression so many times, but now, I'd rather see anything else."


translate English day5_e26d8357:


    nar "My head's been clear for a while now; the heaviness in the air has returned, which I hate.{w} I take a quiet deep breath and exhale."


translate English day5_b629f7c3:


    pl "Did you bring us out of there?"


translate English day5_1c31428f:


    nar "After looking up again, he nods, his face still dark, as though he didn't expect my sudden question."


translate English day5_bf743c38:


    nar "Upon closer inspection, I see a couple bandages on him, too."


translate English day5_6d9f43c9:


    pl "Really? How'd you know?"


translate English day5_ae5a134e:


    sc "I arrange all the newcomers' work. I knew where you were right from the start."


translate English day5_fc95d865:


    sc "But... What I didn't know was that the field would head that way."


translate English day5_c721032c:


    nar "I think back to all the documents before today. Most of them were easy to read--and the tasks were generally just cleaning or disinfecting."


translate English day5_a861ed34:


    nar "I had assumed I'd gotten used to the work here, but now, everything fit together."


translate English day5_b1d25b75:


    nar "So that was why there was a separate folder for today."


translate English day5_684b56e8:


    pl "Maya, did he apologize to you, too?"


translate English day5_ecd2c154:


    my "Huh? Oh, yes... He's been with me until now, too."


translate English day5_dea23149:


    pl "Fine, then.{w} Anyway, I'm not really into the idea of fighting with someone as precarious as you."


translate English day5_503b18fd:


    pl "But I was mostly serious about what I said this morning. It's probably best to fix your habit of bad-mouthing people."


translate English day5_99025227:


    sc "...I doubt I can.{w} It just comes out of me whenever I see your face."


translate English day5_5b42f047:


    pl "What--"


translate English day5_5f2b866a:


    sc "I'm *joking*."


translate English day5_c9def5e8:


    nar "The three of us leave the infirmary room together, and when we see the chairs lined up in front, we find someone with a vivid hair color that clashes with the stark-white ward."


translate English day5_7133a748:


    nar "When she sees us, she waves happily.{w} She's holding a familiar book. I cringe without meaning to."


translate English day5_92d6db79:


    rv "Oh, well... Look what we have here... Hee hee hee."


translate English day5_48e6df75:


    sc "...What's so funny, Lavi?"


translate English day5_19fb0f3e:


    rv "Heh heh heh... Nothing at all, promise."


translate English day5_ac035107:


    pl "Did you come to see me, too?"


translate English day5_ff44a056:


    rv "Yes. I'm glad to see you in good health, little [na]."


translate English day5_33dc5343:


    rv "I'd also like to offer what apology I can."


translate English day5_e45e9b91:


    rv "I lent you that book without a single thought.{w} That was why you all had to face such peril.{w} For that, I am truly sorry."


translate English day5_42d803fa:


    my "What? No, this is all my fault..."


translate English day5_756ae7f1:


    pl "I don't think anyone could have seen this coming."


translate English day5_8d415bc4:


    pl "Also, the Academics Department bishop said it wasn't because of the spell."


translate English day5_4408992f:


    rv "That is correct. There is nothing for you to feel guilty about, Lady Maya."


translate English day5_b08247ef:


    pl "That goes for you too, Lavi.{w} You can be kinda stubborn sometimes, huh?"


translate English day5_ff2a3e4d:


    rv "Oh, dear me... It's rather embarrassing to have the tables turned on me like this!"


translate English day5_82061104:


    pl "Wait a second. If you're here, that means..."


translate English day5_19049afc:


    pl "I've seen four auxiliary bishops in a very short period of time!{w} Wow, I'm so popular!"


translate English day5_bd783065:


    nar "Everyone falls silent at my little joke.{w} I start to panic a bit. Lavi and Securett exchange glances."


translate English day5_aaf3e554:


    rv "To tell the truth... The bishops conferred while you were asleep."


translate English day5_b0e35168:


    pl "Wait, you mean...?"


translate English day5_94cb352a:


    nar "That remark about being a mere onlooker to the miracle I've \"wrought\" comes back to mind."


translate English day5_5a705d7b:


    rv "You're at the center of a major, unprecedented incident.{w} The reasons for which are still unclear..."


translate English day5_a58cefc4:


    rv "We discussed the possibility that this is another divine revelation."


translate English day5_1a7fd738:


    sc "\"Popular\" doesn't even begin to cover it. How are you going to take responsibility for this?"


translate English day5_391af743:


    pl "Responsibility? I..."


translate English day5_3334fc23_2:


    my "......"


translate English day5_5cd891f2:


    nar "Despite Maya being right next to me, I'm so anxious that I can't even think about other people's anxiety."


translate English day5_d7323375:


    nar "Something is happening to my body.{w} Something nobody can explain, least of all myself."


translate English day5_178d2baf:


    nar "If I wasn't scared before, I am now. A cold sweat breaks out on my pale, white palms."


translate English day5_c86c12e8:


    rv "You needn't be so worried. We haven't informed anyone else of this."


translate English day5_eb1e660c_2:


    pl "......"


translate English day5_3e369d3d:


    sc "And we don't intend to, either."


translate English day5_e040599d:


    sc "Spreading outlandish information without a proper grasp on the situation would only make us sound crazy."


translate English day5_3f5e12c3:


    my "That's right, [na2]... And this might not even be anything to worry about, so..."


translate English day5_f218222d:


    pl "But..."


translate English day5_0c3c19d5:


    sc "[na].{w} I know you're worried, but until we get to the truth of the matter, you don't need to think about it so much."


translate English day5_2dde1219:


    sc "Just concentrate on getting some uninterrupted rest for now."


translate English day5_5727d0ca:


    pl "Ha... Been hearing that a lot lately!"


translate English day5_78b62e14:


    pl "Still, you did all tell me about some pretty uncomfortable stuff, and now you're telling me not to get worried about it."


translate English day5_5937b854:


    rv "Little Securett does have a bad habit of failing to hide the truth, after all."


translate English day5_7c1c8e32:


    sc "Urk...!"


translate English day5_a432acce:


    rv "But it's a positive quality to have. And I agree with him, anyway."


translate English day5_8c486911:


    rv "Little [na2], historically speaking, these sorts of incidents mainly end up serving as cautionary tales to not count your chickens before they hatch."


