    "\n When I was little, the villagers would talk about me a lot.{w} Unconcerned about their worries, though, I eventually became an adult, and the scars were still there."


translate English day5_night_8e3e3f53:


    "Over time, the questions and rumors about the scars died down--not only for them, but for me."


translate English day5_night_7bc7ddf5:


    "I'd never thought about how something so normal for me could be completely out of the ordinary for others."


translate English day5_night_1c0e89e0:


    et "It's still hard for me to wrap my head around how the things you know--what you \"obviously\" can't see, what \"obviously\" exists right in front of you--can change so utterly and suddenly."


translate English day5_night_6dc91e02:



    nvl clear
    "\n And since it starts to feel awfully pointless for me to think about it, I knock on the wall to my side once or twice. It makes a hollow sound.{w} There's a little gap underneath a slightly protruding piece of wallpaper; I speak into it several times."


translate English day5_night_e460861f:


    "But I never get an answer, never even sense another person there.{w} Still not home yet? Talk about hard-working."


translate English day5_night_071a5c3c:


    "As I lift my hand to knock again, I hear a noise come back even before hitting the wall."


translate English day5_night_b7877cc9:


    "The sound came from the door that time.{w} My heart flutters a little at the sudden visitation, despite not knowing who it could be yet."


translate English day5_night_6f5daf43:


    et "It's probably because of how empty I felt before."


translate English day5_night_efcbba33:



    nvl clear
    "\n I know it's her there.{w} I don't know why I'm so sure, but it starts my blood flowing again."


translate English day5_night_bf5687d8:


    "Trying my best to calm my pounding heart, I open the door.{w} And there she is."


translate English day5_night_9309a398:


    "Her eyes were on me since before I even opened the door, as if she knew I'd open it."


translate English day5_night_870993cf:


    et "My heart pounds again.{w} But at the same time, her visit comes as no surprise to me."


translate English day5_night_91b4b10f:


    my "Sorry for visiting you so late, [na2]."


translate English day5_night_73a7f1ee:


    pl "It's fine, Maya.{w} What's up?"


translate English day5_night_83b667e6:


    my "I was wondering about my stigmata... I read that spell as well, so...{w} I just got really worried that something had happened."


translate English day5_night_0d012336:


    pl "Oh... I wonder if the Health Department people are still up. If you want, we can go together."


translate English day5_night_997cf5b8:


    nar "I trail off as Maya quietly looks up at me.{w} Her round eyes are trembling, ever so slightly, in mild anxiety."


translate English day5_night_b42b0f65:


    nar "I've seen that face before.{w} Many times, in fact, since we've been together for a while now. That's the face she makes when she wants something from me."


translate English day5_night_84a4037c:


    nar "I fall silent. Even when our eyes meet, she doesn't retreat."


translate English day5_night_ab6b0465:


    nar "In fact, Maya takes a step forward, as if wanting permission to enter the room."


translate English day5_night_aecfba2e:


    nar "In the low moonlight, our elongated shadows slowly overlap."


translate English day5_night_76b2fe88_1:


    nvl clear


translate English day5_night_8fdc4c3a:


    "\n \"Just a look.\""


translate English day5_night_2d17cbcc:


    "Her words enter my head. They sound like they're as much to ease my tension as they are to soothe her own worries."


translate English day5_night_310bc02c:


    "\"I know,\" I reply, shutting my eyes tight."


translate English day5_night_7b5a2ae8:


    "Unable to see anything, I simply hold my breath and wait for her to be done."


translate English day5_night_d1cb9d71:


    et "\"Could you look and see if anything is out of sorts?\""


translate English day5_night_402b15b7:



    nvl clear
    "\n The moment I open my eyes, I realize my ignoble anxiety and premature worries were totally unnecessary."


translate English day5_night_596d2942:


    "A girl's small back is facing me, bathed in the light from outside.{w} I can see her spine and shoulder blades clearly."


translate English day5_night_4ce3de7e:


    "In the pale-white crook of her back are two wounds."


translate English day5_night_c67f1722:


    "They're a pair of stigmata.{w} My mind goes calm--so calm I can't even remember what I must have looked like a moment ago, or what I was thinking then."


translate English day5_night_195e7014:


    et "And the sensation is surprisingly relaxing."


translate English day5_night_56cc594b:



    nvl clear
    "\n I remember when the angel would leave me in those dreams.{w} These are stigmata--the place where wings are supposed to be."


translate English day5_night_354e3a41:


    "I know it's rude of me to think, but the thought comes to me anyway."


translate English day5_night_140a267f:


    "Seeing it up close makes my breath unsteady.{w} I end up hanging my head.{w} Someone like me could never touch her."


translate English day5_night_74cdc438:


    "The sensation of breath on skin.{w} The sound of a forced inhalation."


translate English day5_night_5e0c5eeb:


    et "The fact that she can feel my presence--despite my attempts to hide it--is unbearably embarrassing."


translate English day5_night_a7aaf433:



    nvl clear
    "\n \"Does it look okay?\""


translate English day5_night_08177e1e:


    "Maya's back bends, causing me to shudder and come back to my senses."


translate English day5_night_38385c47:


    "That's a familiar sensation here--like I've been shoved out of a peaceful place and dropped into reality."


translate English day5_night_037f5c60:


    "Maybe I was having a daydream."


translate English day5_night_2a7db2f0:


    "\"Yeah, it's fine. Nothing wrong as far as I can see.\""


translate English day5_night_858c863b:


    "That's right. Nothing there.{w} As I look at the stigmata before me again, my mind settles back down."


translate English day5_night_2458d002:


    et "But my heart is still busily pumping blood through me, like it can't just forget what it felt like.{w} It's as though I just performed some sort of sublime ritual."


